  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.1.7">
<l>tiṭavicum perivaḷi nīrnila mivaimicai</l>
<l>paṭarporuḷ muḻuvatu māyavai yavaitoṟu</l>
<l>muṭaṉmicai yuyireṉak karanteṅkum parantuḷaṉ</l>
<l>cuṭarmiku curutiyu ḷivaiyuṇṭa curaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who exists, spread out everywhere, hidden like the soul in the body,</l>
<l>in all those, being the whole pervading matter/meaning</l>
<l>in these: the firm sky, fire, wind, water, earth,</l>
<l>[he is] the god who is in these [words of] aural teaching abounding in lustre.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
